svg class=\"hurry-check\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        <circle cx=\"14\" cy=\"14\" r=\"13\" fill=\"#c0607a\"/>\n        <path d=\"M8 14.5L12 18.5L20 10\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n      </svg>\n      <span>Get salon-quality brows, skin, and style from the comfort of your own home.</span>\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"hurry-bullet\">\n      <svg class=\"hurry-check\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        <circle cx=\"14\" cy=\"14\" r=\"13\" fill=\"#c0607a\"/>\n        <path d=\"M8 14.5L12 18.5L20 10\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n      </svg>\n      <span>Stop overpaying at salons — get real results with affordable products delivered to your door.</span>\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"hurry-bullet\">\n      <svg class=\"hurry-check\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        <circle cx=\"14\" cy=\"14\" r=\"13\" fill=\"#c0607a\"/>\n        <path d=\"M8 14.5L12 18.5L20 10\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n      </svg>\n      <span>Turn heads and receive compliments — because you deserve to feel beautiful every day.</span>\n    </li>\n\n  </ul>\n</div>",
